OL,3,CMourners gather in Milan to bid final
OL,4,Cfarewell to Giorgio Armani
OL,6,FThe funeral of Giorgio Armani took
OL,7,Fplace in his home village of Rivalta,
OL,8,Fnear Milan, in a private ceremony on
OL,9,FMonday afternoon.
OL,11,FThe Italian fashion designer died aged
OL,12,F91 on Thursday, September 4,
OL,13,Fsurrounded by family.
OL,15,FThe funeral follows three days of
OL,16,Fremembrance, where more than 15,000
OL,17,Fmourners queued outside the Armani/
OL,18,FTeatro to view Armani's closed coffin.
