OL,6,FThey included top names in fashion,
OL,7,Fpolitics, film and sports ` worlds
OL,8,Fwith which Armani was closely entwined.
OL,10,FThe Mayor of Milan, Giuseppe Sala,
OL,11,Fdeclared Monday a day of mourning in
OL,12,Fhonour of the late designer.
OL,14,FArmani stores will also be closed in
OL,15,Fthe afternoon as a mark of respect.
