OL,3,CMourners gather in Milan to bid final
OL,4,Cfarewell to Giorgio Armani
OL,6,FBorn in 1934, Armani initially studied
OL,7,Fmedicine before moving into fashion
OL,8,Fduring the 1960s and setting up his
OL,9,Fown label alongside his partner Sergio
OL,10,FGaleotti in 1975.
OL,12,FStarting with an unlined jacket,
OL,13,Fsimple trousers and an urban palette,
OL,14,FArmani put Italian ready-to-wear style
OL,15,Fon the global fashion map in the late
OL,16,F1970s, creating the relaxed silhouette
OL,17,Fthat defined his brand for the next
OL,18,Fhalf-century.
