OL,3,CMourners gather in Milan to bid final
OL,4,Cfarewell to Giorgio Armani
OL,6,FA statement from his family and
OL,7,Femployees read: "In this company, we
OL,8,Fhave always felt like part of a
OL,9,Ffamily. Today, with deep emotion, we
OL,10,Ffeel the void left by the one who
OL,11,Ffounded and nurtured this family with
OL,12,Fvision, passion, and dedication.
OL,14,F"But it is precisely in his spirit
OL,15,Fthat we, the employees and the family
OL,16,Fmembers who have always worked
OL,17,Falongside Mr Armani, commit to
OL,18,Fprotecting what he built and to
OL,19,Fcarrying his company forward in his
OL,20,Fmemory, with respect, responsibility,
OL,21,Fand love."
