OL,3,CMourners gather in Milan to bid final
OL,4,Cfarewell to Giorgio Armani
OL,6,FEnglish supermodel Naomi Campbell took
OL,7,Fto social media to share her tribute
OL,8,Fdescribing Armani as a man of
OL,9,F"precision unmatched" and
OL,10,F"perfectionist in the purest sense".
OL,12,FSister of the late Gianni Versace,
OL,13,FDonatella, wrote on Instagram: "The
OL,14,Fworld lost a giant today. He made
OL,15,Fhistory and will be remembered
OL,16,Fforever."
