OL,4,Cfarewell to Giorgio Armani
OL,6,FAt the time of his death, Armani had
OL,7,Fbuilt an empire worth more than $10
OL,8,Fbillion (#7.4 billion), spanning not
OL,9,Fonly fashion but also accessories,
OL,10,Fhomeware, perfumes, cosmetics, books,
OL,11,Fflowers and even chocolates, placing
OL,12,Fhim among the world's top 200
OL,13,Fbillionaires, according to Forbes.
OL,15,FHe also owned bars, clubs, restaurants
OL,16,Fand his own basketball team, EA7
OL,17,FEmporio Armani Milan, better known as
OL,18,FOlimpia Milano.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
