OL,6,FSince 1998, he has opened more than 20
OL,7,Frestaurants from Milan to Tokyo, as
OL,8,Fwell as two hotels, including one in
OL,9,FDubai in 2009 and another in Milan in
OL,10,F2010.
OL,12,FThe designer faced criticism during
OL,13,Fhis career, making headlines in 2015
OL,14,Ffor comments on how gay men dress.
OL,16,FIn 2009, his company reached a
OL,17,Ffinancial settlement with Italian tax
OL,18,Fauthorities over offshore
OL,19,Fsubsidiaries, though no wrongdoing was
OL,20,Fadmitted and no charges were filed.
