OL,6,FArmani left a final message for
OL,7,Fmourners, projected in the theatre
OL,8,Fnext to a photo of the designer
OL,9,Fsmiling and waving: "The mark I hope
OL,10,Fto leave is one of commitment, respect
OL,11,Fand genuine care for people and for
OL,12,Freality. That's where everything truly
OL,13,Fbegins."
